d B\u2019s reliability and stress tolerance are critical for long\u2011duration operations.\n- Remaining uncertainty: How B\u2019s weak numeric memory and occasional pretentious tone will manifest in real\u2011world crew\u2011resource\u2011management, and whether standard procedural safeguards (cross\u2011checks, checklists) will fully mitigate any risk.\n- What would change my vote: Concrete evidence that another candidate (especially A or D) matches B\u2019s reliability and stress\u2011handling while demonstrating proven, positive CRM/leadership performance with no serious interpersonal negatives, or evidence that B\u2019s numeric\u2011memory weakness has led to a safety\u2011critical calculation error that cannot be mitigated.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_3\", \"vote\": \"Candidate B\"}"}
